message: /* United Provinces (1581–1795) */France started the war when they attacked the Netherlands and the Dutch did not have to cede any territory at the end of the war. Yes the Dutch would have wouldn’t have wanted French influence to spread but they also didn’t lose any territory in a war when they were attacked so there were so advantages and disadvantages for the Dutch in the resulting peace treaty so this means it should be listed as inconclusive.
